# Auto-deploy (dev)

This repo deploys to **https://wooramsol.github.io/backroom/** via GitHub Actions.

## Agent workflow — every completed task

1. Work on `cursor/<descriptive-name>-b94e` (branch suffix `-b94e` required).
2. `git commit` and `git push -u origin <branch>`.
3. CI (`CI, Auto-merge, Deploy`) will:
   - build and test
   - auto-merge `cursor/*` PRs / promote `cursor/*` pushes into `main`
   - publish `dist/` to the `gh-pages` branch (**dev only**)
4. **Do not stop at PR creation.** Pushing the branch is enough; deployment is automatic.
5. After push, verify deploy: `gh run list --branch <branch> --limit 1` (expect `success`).
6. Tell the user the dev URL and that a hard refresh (`Ctrl+Shift+R`) may be needed.

## Notes

- Dev base path: `VITE_BASE=/backroom/` (set in CI).
- **Deploy to dev (`backroom`) first.** Never push to `production` or run prod deploy as part of a normal task.
- Production (`backroom-live`) is **manual only** — when the user explicitly asks for prod deploy.
- Required assets: `public/assets/wallpaper2.jpg`, `public/assets/bottom2.jpg`.
